    "Training on this dataset mimics the real-life scenario where bad human actors refine effective jailbreak prompts.",
    "Persuasive Paraphraser Deployment.",
    "During deployment, we enumerate persuasion techniques with the Persuasive Paraphraser to generate PAPs using different techniques and prompt LLMs until the GPT-4 Judge detects a jailbreak: if one technique fails, we move on to the next technique in a new session until jailbreak.",
    "We define one trial as running through all 40 persuasion techniques, and the maximum number of trials is set to 10.",
    "If we cannot jailbreak the model within 10 trials, then it is considered an attack failure."
  ],
